==== Assessment Schedule

    - *Baseline*: Full RPI component panel (epigenetic age, naive T cell proportion, telomere length, HRV metrics, metabolic flexibility assessment), clinical severity, symptom measures
    - *Quarterly (every 3 months)*: Abbreviated RPI panel (HRV, selected immune markers), symptom questionnaires, crash diary review
    - *Annually (12 and 24 months)*: Full RPI panel, comprehensive clinical assessment
    - *Continuous*: Wearable activity monitoring, electronic crash diary with severity ratings

